Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:02.12,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}N-Non è niente di che....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:04.54,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Senpai Chigusa, buona giornata!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:05.58,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}A domani!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:06.21,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Sì!
