Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:20.48,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}E se... mi toccherà... sul serio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:29.32,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Se lo facesse... io potrei...
