Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:35.75,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Anche se non sei in una posa particolare, sei venuta molto sexy, non credi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:39.26,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}So che riesci a capirlo anche da sola.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.47,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Non è vero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.01,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Bene, continuiamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:44.97,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Va bene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:51.94,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Nana, apri un po' le gambe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:53.90,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Così.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:56.48,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Guarda qui, Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:57.98,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Davvero...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:58.73,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Così, bene...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.57,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Davvero, sono...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.61,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Nana, ancora una volta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.45,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Sono...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:09.29,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Davvero sono così... pervertita?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.37,Alternativo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Incredibile...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.66,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Sei proprio una pervertita.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:16.92,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Sei così erotica con quel costume da bagno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:21.17,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Faresti perdere la testa a chiunque.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.51,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Molto bene, Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.76,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Magnifica, sei così arrapante...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:28.89,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Nana...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.89,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Hai delle belle ascelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:37.52,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Anche la zona intorno al tuo ombelico non è male, Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:38.07,Alternativo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}S-Scemo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:42.95,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Hai delle cosce molto morbide e tornite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:44.70,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}S-Scemo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.58,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Non ti preoccupare, mi accerterò di fotografare tutto per bene.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:52.41,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Non fare così, Nana. Guarda verso di me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.00,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.42,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Guarda la fotocamera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.93,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}In questo modo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:18.23,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Molto bene, adesso prova ad accovacciarti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:22.78,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Eh? A... Accovacciarmi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.11,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Accovacciarmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.28,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Non così, Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:32.08,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Devi aprire le gambe quando ti accovacci.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:33.86,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Le gambe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.54,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Cosa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:39.46,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}A-Aprire... le gambe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:40.71,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:46.47,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Così...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:52.51,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:11.33,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ne hai già scattate tante in questa posa, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:12.79,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Che vergogna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.50,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ah, aspetta, Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.12,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Resta così.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.67,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Resta così...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:24.21,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}solo un altro po', va bene?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.15,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}No! Kaoru, aspetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:42.44,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Che... Che stai facendo, Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:46.19,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}N-No! Ka...o...ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:49.82,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Che c'è, Nana?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:52.49,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}C-Cosa succede?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:54.99,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}È quello che avevamo stabilito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:57.12,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}L'hai dimenticato?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:15:00.50,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Avevamo deciso che ti avrei fotografata legata con una corda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:04.63,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}E poi, Nana, ti fidi di me, vero?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.80,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Sì... penso di potermi fidare...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.64,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Kaoru, aspetta! Che fai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:20.14,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}In questo modo sarà più eccitante.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:22.86,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}F-Fidati di me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:25.11,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Allora, Nana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:26.53,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Cosa devo fare?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:31.16,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Il mio cuore... sta battendo all'impazzata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:36.41,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Kaoru... continua.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.21,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Questa... Questa sensazione...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:45.59,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Mi sta legando...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:48.46,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Sto venendo legata da lui...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.59,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Dannazione! Maledetto Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.89,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Io...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.54,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Mi sto...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:59.52,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Mi sto eccitando molto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.52,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:05.90,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Stai da dio, Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:09.65,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Sento la corda stretta sul mio corpo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:13.49,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}E poi, questa benda sugli occhi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:19.04,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}mi fa immaginare tutti i lineamenti \Ndel mio corpo, anche quelli a cui non penso mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:24.42,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Nana, sei bellissima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:27.17,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Quella corda ti sta benissimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:29.34,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}E io che ne so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:33.93,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ah, già! È vero, non puoi vedere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:38.81,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Allora ci darò dentro con le foto, e poi dopo te le farò vedere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.10,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Eh? C-Cosa sta fotografando?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.77,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Il collo? La schiena?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:51.40,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}D-Dove sta inquadrando?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:54.15,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}D-Dove, Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:59.12,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Uffa! Non riesco a smettere di cercare la sua presenza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:02.29,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Il suo respiro, il suo calore corporeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.62,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}È tutta colpa di questa benda!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:09.38,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Kaoru, dove sei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:13.59,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Kao...ru? Kaoru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.47,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Kao...ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:23.06,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:23.85,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ka...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:24.48,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:28.15,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Kao...! Fermati! Kao...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:33.15,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Nana, adoro quell'espressione.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:36.36,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}È proprio quella l'espressione che volevo catturare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:40.78,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}No! Aspetta, Kaoru! Fermati!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.38,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}No, Kao...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:57.05,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Kaoru! Idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.01,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ahia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:01.31,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Pensavo ti sarebbe piaciuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:02.93,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Nana, sei arrabbiata?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:06.31,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}C-C-Certo che lo sono! C-Che diavolo stavi pensando?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.06,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Però...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.69,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Eh? Nana, non te ne sei accorta?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.90,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Nana, sei così eccitata che ti si sono induriti i capezzoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.53,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}N-N-Non è vero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.57,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Eh? Non capisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:23.62,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}N-Nonostante... Nonostante sia il mio corpo, non riesco...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:23.62,Alternativo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Va bene.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:27.41,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Lascerò che lo veda con i tuoi stessi occhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:28.67,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Vedi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.17,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Sono diventati...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:33.34,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I miei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:38.22,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Così belli duri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:41.85,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I-I miei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:49.81,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:54.48,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Guarda l'espressione del tuo viso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:59.99,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Posso mandare questa foto a tutti? Guarda, si vede solo il tuo viso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:57.94,Alternativo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Io... Io...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:00.91,Alternativo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Quello è... Quello è...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:05.29,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Quello è... il mio... viso...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:08.29,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Il mio corpo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:11.17,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}La mia espressione...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.63,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Io... Io...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:21.18,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:27.27,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Fermati, Kaoru... per favore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:37.36,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}M-Me l'avevi promesso, Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:42.36,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}La regola diceva che se io avessi detto di no, tu ti saresti fermato!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:44.03,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}K-Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.29,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Avevo detto così?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:55.79,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Guarda, dai un'occhiata.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:20:03.43,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I-Il tuo viso, i tuoi capezzoli e \Nil tuo corpo stanno implorando di continuare.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:08.10,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Davanti agli altri fingi di essere una brava ragazza.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:12.02,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ti comporti come se non ti interessassero le cose erotiche.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:18.02,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Però la vera Nana non è così.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:22.70,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Voglio che tutti quanti possano vederlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:26.74,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}E quando questo avverrà...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:32.21,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Sapranno quanto sei pervertita, Nana.
